author: Al Jazeera
title: In Pictures: Thousands rally in US against coronavirus curbs
description: Protests staged across the US calling for the lifting of stay-at-home orders imposed by state governors.
content:
Thousands of people across the United States have protested against "stay-at-home" orders after President Donald Trump encouraged people to defy coronavirus lockdown imposed by state governors.
